"{\"uid\": \"independent.co.uk-sport-olympics-raygun-breaking-olympics-paris-australia-b2596923.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Notifications can be managed in browser preferences.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 52, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in  Swipe for next article  The Australian athlete was the subject of criticism following her performance at Paris 2024  I would like to be emailed about offers, events and updates from The Independent.\", \"from\": 54, \"to\": 390, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 216, \"end\": 230, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Australian\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.5673362869053745e-22, \"text\": \"The Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Australian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Australian\"}, {\"begin\": 297, \"end\": 307, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0334946429074643e-13, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy notice  Australian breakdancer Rachael Gunn, known as Raygun, called the response to herParis 2024Olympicsperformance \\\"devastating\\\", after she was widely criticised following her debut at the Games.\", \"from\": 391, \"to\": 605, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 415, \"end\": 425, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9885384672288658, \"rank\": 0.00837878674620279, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 438, \"end\": 445, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\", \"score\": 0.9999999996712177, \"rank\": 3.281522984565949e-10, \"text\": \"Rachael\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\"}, {\"begin\": 446, \"end\": 450, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9978790782758802, \"rank\": 0.0020410441003911733, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}, {\"begin\": 461, \"end\": 467, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.091195968022429e-21, \"text\": \"Raygun\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 36-year-old, who is a university lecturer in Sydney,lost all three of her round-robin contestsby a combined score of 54-0 and wasridiculed on social media.\", \"from\": 607, \"to\": 766, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 656, \"end\": 662, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"score\": 0.9999822718180293, \"rank\": 1.623965914602477e-05, \"text\": \"Sydney\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And Gunn has since spoken candidly about the abuse she received.\", \"from\": 768, \"to\": 832, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 772, \"end\": 776, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9978790782758802, \"rank\": 0.0020410441003911733, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking in anInstagram video, she said: \\\"I really appreciated the positivity and I am glad I was able to bring some joy into your lives - that's what I hoped.\", \"from\": 834, \"to\": 993, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Well, I went out there and I had fun - I did take it very seriously.\", \"from\": 995, \"to\": 1064, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I worked my butt off preparing for the Olympics and I gave my all.\", \"from\": 1065, \"to\": 1131, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Truly.\", \"from\": 1132, \"to\": 1138, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And I am honoured to have been a part of the Australian Olympic team; to be a part of breaking's Olympic debut.\\\"\", \"from\": 1140, \"to\": 1253, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1186, \"end\": 1209, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9873651690715508, \"rank\": 0.012796512702918091, \"text\": \"Australian Olympic team\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_at_the_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After Gunn's performance, a petition was created calling for an apology from the athlete and Australia's Olympic chef de mission Anna Meares.\", \"from\": 1255, \"to\": 1396, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1261, \"end\": 1265, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9978790782758802, \"rank\": 0.0020410441003911733, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}, {\"begin\": 1348, \"end\": 1357, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9947316287029154, \"rank\": 0.0017594869601661677, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 1384, \"end\": 1395, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Meares\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anna Meares\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Meares\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Meares\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It has been signed more than 50,000 times and derides Gunn and Meares for \\\"attempting to gaslight the public and undermining the efforts of genuine athletes\\\".\", \"from\": 1397, \"to\": 1555, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Gunn defended herself after claims that she was not of the required standard to compete at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1557, \"to\": 1661, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1557, \"end\": 1561, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9978790782758802, \"rank\": 0.0020410441003911733, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Bit of a fun fact for you: there are actually no points in breaking,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1663, \"to\": 1743, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If you want to see how the judges scored me compared to my opponents, you can actually see the comparison percentages across the five criteria on Olympics.com, external - all the results are there.\", \"from\": 1745, \"to\": 1943, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1892, \"end\": 1904, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 0.9998571708780887, \"rank\": 0.00014284952500434207, \"text\": \"Olympics.com\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I'd really like to ask the press to please stop harassing my family, my friends, the Australian breaking community and the broader street dance community.\", \"from\": 1945, \"to\": 2100, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2031, \"end\": 2041, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9885384672288658, \"rank\": 0.00837878674620279, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Everyone has been through a lot as a result of this, so I ask you to please respect their privacy.\\\"\", \"from\": 2102, \"to\": 2202, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Join thought-provoking conversations, follow other Independent readers and see their replies  Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in\", \"from\": 2204, \"to\": 2434, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2255, \"end\": 2266, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 7.715649771836194e-13, \"text\": \"Independent\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\"}]}]}"